            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;      欧洲股市早段下跌。英国富时100指数报10,225.34点，跌79.81点(0.77%)；德国DAX指数报23,346.03点，跌243.62点(1.03%)；法国CAC 40指数报7,891.58点，跌92.86点(1.16%)。  (WL)</span>\n</div>",
